19:47.320 --> 19:48.387
It's him.
It's Merlot.

19:48.389 --> 19:50.189
He's getting away!

19:50.191 --> 19:56.061
♪♪

19:56.063 --> 19:57.830
Good!

20:02.069 --> 20:03.869
Thank you, A.J.

20:03.871 --> 20:06.071
Don't worry about it,
Mr. Clef.

20:06.073 --> 20:09.140
Hey, it doesn't matter
that we lost.

20:09.142 --> 20:11.276
You should all feel really --
Hang on, Mr. Clef.

20:11.278 --> 20:13.344
Announcer: May I have
your attention, please.

20:13.346 --> 20:16.548
The winning team
has been disqualified.

20:16.550 --> 20:17.816
A [bleep] [bleep]
has been found

20:17.818 --> 20:20.351
